title: Dean Morrison and Bruce Irons during the 2006 Pipe Masters
description:
Check out footage shot from the deck of the Volcom House in December of 2006 during the Pipeline Masters. Dean Morrison and Bruce Irons pull into some heavy pits during their early round heats in big Pipeline surf.

- Music -
Song: "Marooned"
